name: Single VM
description:
The Single-VM blueprint allows provisioning of infrastructure on the AHV platform through a simple guided flow. Users can enter basic VM configuration details, such as 
* VM Image
*  VCPU 
*  Memory
*  Number of Cores per VCPU
*  Network 
  
In addition to others at runtime to launch a VM that suits their requirement. Both, Linux and Windows guest operating systems are available for the VMs.
author: Nutanix
